S(\vec \ell)=\{s\in S:k_i(s)=\ell_i\text{ for }i=1\dots,x\}\;.
|S(\vec\ell)|=\binom{xy}{\ell_1,\dots,\ell_x}=\frac{(xy)!}{\ell_1!\ell_2!\dots\ell_x!}\;.
